data.title: Jean S. Dieudonne
data.meta_description:
My name is Jean S. Dieudonne, and I'm the author of two books. the first one is "Who Says your Future Dictates on your Past?",  " Deep into the Realm of Spirit", Operating in the Prophetic, and One life to Live One Purpose to Pursue.
If you are looking to read some good books, please try any of these four books, and I can guaranty that you will love them both. 

I grew up in Haiti, but I moved to the USA at the age of 17. My life story is the reason why I wrote my first book. I tell my story of my life in Haiti and USA, and where I'm now. This alone will help you to know that your past doesn't determine your future.. 

Get your copy of my books and I can promise you won't regret any of them. 

God bless you...
